Package nsk.enhanced.System.Hibernate

Class Event

java.lang.Object
nsk.enhanced.System.Hibernate.Event
@Entity public class Event extends Object

The Event class represents an event occurring in the server, stored in the `surveillance_events` database table. This class is responsible for capturing and managing various types of events related to players, including their locations, worlds, and additional data.

The Event class links together several other entities, including Character, WorldEntity, and EventDetails, to provide a comprehensive record of player actions and state changes in the game.
